Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}"Everyone must have someone\Nthey want to kill."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}l think this is what started it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}We wrote the name of the person\Nwe want to kill half-jokingly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Asao Hosokawa"\N{\i1}and secretly showed each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}Right after that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}The name l wrote was\NYutaro Yamagiwa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}People are murdered\None after next...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Masao Tanaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}They said he got a note that says,\N"lt is your turn to kill!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}People are cornered...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The name l wrote\Non my piece of paper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}was Misato Akaike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I heard you played a dangerous\Ngame at the residents' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think we should tell the police\Nabout the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}But still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Maybe we would all be treated\Nas a murderer for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I did nothing, so l don't want to be\Ntreated as an accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}We didn't talk to the police...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l wrote on the ballot paper that\Nl wanted to kill Yoshihiko Hakamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}And one more person died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Yoshihiko Hakamada"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Episode 6"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Don't panic, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}that isn't the only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You startled me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You went to meet Nana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Anyway, when did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You hit on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But you're married, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, Nana is pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so l can understand why\Nyou want to make a move on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nana is my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, l am happy that\Nmy wife is popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but l had no idea that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l think we do get along, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We even have the same taste\Nin women! The same!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Your wife is popular,\Ndoesn't it worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}One worries because\Nhe hasn't had enough training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No, it's image training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"If my beloved wife has an affair."\NThat's the image training l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}In the end, my plan is to love\NNana more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's the only one l have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Even if you're serious about\Npursuing Nana,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l'll just give her even more love\Nthan you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We worked together for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}then we met again after a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I had no idea\Nthat she was your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What? "l had no idea"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It should be,\N"l had no idea, sorry," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Okay, we're friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}We'll give you the latest update\Non the case.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}In 1991, when Mr Yoshihiko Hakamada\Nwas 18 years old,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}he won the Junon Super Boy Contest\NGrand Prix Award...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}When l was slim,\Npeople said l looked quite like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think l've seen him somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Hey, it's Yoshihiko Hakamada!\NYou don't know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}That's not what l mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Look, it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"101 Yuzuru Kuzumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He looks like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Wait, it's that condo again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, we'll concentrate on our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Murder of Kuramae Condo's Couple"\NWhat's your current recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Recommendation"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}This guy, l think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I still can't verify his alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}on the night\NMr and Mrs Akaike were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Room 203, Xinyi Lin,\Nstudent from China"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Your Turn to Kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}lt isn't your fault, Mr Kuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}lt's obviously my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's because l wrote\NYoshihiko Hakamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I kept wishing him dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but l actually think that\Nhe's a very good actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think he was a good actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Who drew your ballot paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yoshihiko Hakamada was a good actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mr Kuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Are you threatened by anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}LIke when Mr Fujii was threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No, l haven't received any notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Moreover, l don't know the man\Nwhose name was on my paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so how can l kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Will you show me\Nthe piece of paper again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's "Asao Hosokawa", l presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes, the first name is Asao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I wrote the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So, please, don't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If anyone threatens you,\Nplease talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mr Kuzumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}All of these aren't a trap you set,\Nright? Or are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Suddenly, people started dying\Nthe day you moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The property manager died\Non the very same day you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh? Mr Kuzumi? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You hit on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No, we're talking about the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh... The murder-swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}They obviously are going to\Nmake a deal with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What did they carry here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Someone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Asao Hosokawa"\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am this man's trainer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Big Bro will be shocked\Nif he's killed for hitting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Hit on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}That's how you knew him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- I...\N- Wait... l'll guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Orangutan Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nana, you're actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}To him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry, l don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Who is married to whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You've asked me to\Nregister our marriage many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but l still haven't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Because l can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm still married to him\Non the marriage records.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Should l leave you two alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No! Please stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I... I'm a bit upset\Nif no one else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Wait, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}May l hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think l told you\Nthat l was divorced,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and that my ex-husband is Mr Hosokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He's the managing director\Nof my previous design company
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and he was a nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But many things happened\Nafter we got married,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- so we decided to get divorced.\N- Many things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry, may l finish this first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yeah... Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}There was one thing that\Nl could never forgive him for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}ls it many or just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry... I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We decided to get divorced,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but he said\Nhe didn't want to see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and asked me to post him\Nthe divorce form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So l did what he asked\Nand let him submit the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Then, when l went to\Nrenew my driver's licence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l found out that\Nthe form wasn't submitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Did you tell Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I told him over and over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but he made up excuses every time\Nand avoided the topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Shota, after you proposed to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l told him that\Nl wanted to marry someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He accepted it at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but he still didn't submit the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Of course,\Nit was partly my fault too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}After l started working freelance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l still took jobs from his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So when l think\Nabout our future life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l just couldn't insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Ouch! lt hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am sorry!\Nl know they are all excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- It's a bull's eye!\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's been a while since l hit\Nthe bull's eye at Orangutan Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I was just going to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Your ex-husband is actually Big Bro,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and you wrote his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes! l guessed it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Shota...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Shota, don't apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You've been worrying about\Nsomething so serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but l had absolutely no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'll kneel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I hurt my semitendinosus a bit\Nduring training today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so l will just bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- So, Mr Kuzumi.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please don't kill this man\Nby mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nana had loved him so much\Nthat she was married to him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I won't kill him, so may l go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"lt is your turn to kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}lt has come already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Obey the rules properly"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l met him the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}because l didn't know\Nwho drew my piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I just wanted to see if he was\Nattacked or harassed in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So we're all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Anyway, is anything else\Nworrying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You might as well\Ntell me everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Room 302's occupant"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l think you might be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}Telling him more might\Nturn my worries into reality,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}so l couldn't say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Let's start from doing what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Is there anyone you can talk to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh, detectives.\NWhat's the matter today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We'd like to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Actually, Miss Seno's fingerprints\Nwere left in the late Akaikes' flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, we have done some digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You brought the old lady home\Nwhen she fell from her wheelchair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So, where were kind Miss Seno\Nand the two gentlemen on that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The three of us went for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- a car trip.\N- Dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We took a drive and had dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I see. Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Kojima Kids English Class"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mr Ukita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Should we worry about the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry for making you do this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I don't do this for you two,\Nit's just for Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No, it isn't even for Airi either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's for the promise l made\Nto her late mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I won't let Airi have\Na criminal record.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}And you should\Npull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You'll marry her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes. l am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}When will you be back next time?\NTell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You haven't been back for so long,\Nand you'll just leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You told me to leave\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I want children!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What? Whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's too late to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Let's start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You know that isn't the problem,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We can go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If we have children, we can go back\Nto the happy days...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You're out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- I'll race you.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Why?\N- Because you run faster than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l'll start two seconds later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Two seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Fumi, Kazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I made Bavarois. Let's have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am already full.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Then, Kazu, let's have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Ouch!\N- Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It hurts! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Why am l always the lonely one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Why are you all here so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We want to talk about the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Let's talk somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What do you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If we all know what name each person\Nwrote and who drew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}then maybe we can prevent\Nmore murders from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Although I'm not convinced that\Nnone of you want to tell the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If anyone dies because of the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}it's possible that everyone\Nparticipated is just as guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But doesn't it make you feel guilty\Nif you don't do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I know what you mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but there's no way to find out what\Nthe caretaker and Mrs Akaike wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes, you are right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We think that it isn't\Ntotally useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I didn't even tell my wife\Nabout the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We hope you would convince the other\Nresidents for us if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You mean everyone here\Nagrees on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please. lf you say it, they will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}All these years,\Nl've been meddlesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}during the residents' meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But l won't be anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I want to use my time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}for my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think we can only create\Nan opportunity to ask them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yeah, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I wonder what happened to Mr Tamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He is like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We've made no progress at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nana, who do you think will be\Nnext to get killed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}in the murder-swap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If there really is\Na murder-swap going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and it actually goes in that order,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}the person whose name you wrote\Ngets killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}then you get threatened,\Nand forced to kill the next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}And this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}That means Mr Ukita\Nkilled Yoshihiko Hakamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Ukita kills Yoshihiko Hakamada"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l don't know.\NI'm not confident at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The news said that\Nhe was attacked by several people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But Mr Ukita has two underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But you see, if Mrs Akaike was\Nkilled by the Chinese girl, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry, let's stop this.\NMost of these are groundless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I believe what you deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think there are other things\Nthat we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}That's right, Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If he's killed,\Nyou could be arrested too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please don't kill this man\Nby mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.07,0:22:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think we can trust Mr Kuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Anyway, you'll see him at the gym,\Nwon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'll try to talk to him calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Shota! Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry, I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Today, l made...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Talk if you can keep up with me.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Do you drink protein shake daily?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I made this protein shake myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The milk is additive-free and--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l am happy, but you've been\Ngiving me too many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so can this be the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You see, l don't know what\Nthank-you gift to give girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and l shouldn't take too much.\NThat's what Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}That's what my wife said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Thank you for this. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.58,0:23:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You lied about hitting on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You said l hit on her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please break up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.35,0:23:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mr Tezuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please break up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You've trained me very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Listen, l am Nana's legal husband
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and she is having\Nan affair with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You even bought a flat\Nand live together,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}now you can't make up any excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If l sue you, you'll pay me\Na large sum of alimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.45,0:24:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and Nana will lose the job\Nthat earns her money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You are nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.63,0:24:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I've checked how much you earn too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You will both be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.96,0:24:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I will still call you Big Bro.\NBig Bro--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.08,0:24:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, we are brothers in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.96,0:24:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You'll punch me?\NPunch me and get fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.01,0:25:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.39,0:25:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l love everything about Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I love Nana now and l will continue\Nto love her in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.93,0:25:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}and that includes the time that\Nspans her whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.77,0:25:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.89,0:25:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l even love the days that\NNana was living with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.51,0:25:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}When l say l love Nana,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.07,0:25:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l also mean that l love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.53,0:25:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You'll break me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.37,0:25:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.97,0:25:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So l will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.25,0:25:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.29,0:25:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If you feel that someone wants to\Nkill you, tell me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.73,0:26:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Why would anyone want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.73,0:26:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I told you about the game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.21,0:26:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nana wrote your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.61,0:26:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.97,0:26:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But l will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.69,0:26:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I feel guilty\Nevery time l watch the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.93,0:26:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It isn't your fault, Mr Kuzumi.\Nlt's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.43,0:26:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I want to think it is too!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.43,0:26:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh, darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.71,0:26:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Names Revelation Meeting"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.19,0:26:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nobody comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.75,0:26:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I guess they really don't want to\Ntell others the names they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.35,0:26:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, we have been\Nkeeping ours a secret too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.67,0:26:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Why don't we tell each other now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.75,0:26:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I will go first, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.83,0:27:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I wrote...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.33,0:27:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"My first boyfriend."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.90,0:27:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Your first boyfriend? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.74,0:27:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He had seen\Nmy most embarrassing moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.90,0:27:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so l wanted him to die before\Nanyone finds out about my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.66,0:27:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It is nothing serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.38,0:27:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}On the train station platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.82,0:27:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l forced him to kiss me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.10,0:27:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, l didn't write an actual name,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.22,0:27:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so l don't think he'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.58,0:27:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.72,0:27:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}By the way,\Nthe ballot paper l drew says,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.52,0:27:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"People who don't give up\Ntheir seats on the train."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.84,0:27:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}lt sounds like Mr Tamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.66,0:27:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yeah, he doesn't accept\Nanything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.54,0:27:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sounds like\Nwhat Mr Tamiya would write.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.10,0:28:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I wrote the name of the professor\Nof my university tutor group.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.46,0:28:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}His name is Hayakawa\Nand we're on very bad terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.23,0:28:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm now in my third year,\Nbut he already said
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.23,0:28:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}he would certainly make me repeat\Nno matter what thesis l write.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.18,0:28:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}How mean of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.18,0:28:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But l wrote "Professor",\Nit's obvious that l wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.94,0:28:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Xinyi is a student too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.34,0:28:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But Xinyi probably wrote the owner\Nof the Bhutanese diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.78,0:28:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.90,0:28:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}And l think l told you the name on\Nthe piece of paper l drew,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.62,0:28:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}it was Oda Nobunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.62,0:28:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Who wrote the name as a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.98,0:28:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But isn't the answer to this\Nquite clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.23,0:28:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's someone who hates Nobunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.86,0:28:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nobody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.14,0:28:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Among the residents,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.70,0:28:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}there could be offspring of\Nlmagawa Yoshimoto or Takeda Shingen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.87,0:28:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I don't know much\Nabout Japanese history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:28:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Yes?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.07,0:29:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What about you, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.23,0:29:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The piece of paper l drew says,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.91,0:29:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Takafumi Kono", in Hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.59,0:29:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- You don't know him?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.67,0:29:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I don't know him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.78,0:29:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}And the name l wrote was...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Asao Hosokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.14,0:29:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}And l drew the piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.51,0:29:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Who is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.21,0:29:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.37,0:29:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}lt's someone l knew at my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.97,0:29:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.01,0:29:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The reason that Nana wants\Nmy acquaintance to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.41,0:29:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, it's a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.19,0:29:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but it's just a side of her\Nthat you haven't seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.91,0:29:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}This is Black Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.27,0:29:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.55,0:29:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.55,0:29:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Ms Kitagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.35,0:29:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l think it's time to\Ntell Mr Ukita everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.70,0:30:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's still early.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.47,0:30:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I wouldn't tell him if l could.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.75,0:30:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But l think the police has realised.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.15,0:30:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.39,0:30:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- So what?\N- So Mr Ukita...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.61,0:30:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You do know what matters most now,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.14,0:30:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.82,0:30:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.58,0:30:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I understand why the other people\Ndon't want to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.94,0:30:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}it's possible that we'd be\Nin the same room
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.54,0:30:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}with whoever murdered\NMr and Mrs Akaike.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.34,0:30:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Are you not afraid, Ms Kitagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.14,0:30:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.65,0:30:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l came here for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.38,0:30:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I fear that it could even harm Sora\Nat this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.97,0:31:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, among those who participated\Nin the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.86,0:31:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}there shouldn't be anyone\Nwho would harm Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.86,0:31:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.94,0:31:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The name l wrote\Non the ballot paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.10,0:31:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}was Mrs Kayo Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.34,0:31:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Kayo Kojima"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.42,0:31:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l didn't want to say that l wrote\Nthe name of our neighbour,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.38,0:31:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but l think you all know that\Nshe isn't in her right mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.90,0:31:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yasu said he was afraid\Nto be on his own, so l...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.38,0:31:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}This woman called Sora "Yasu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.99,0:31:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}She gave him another name and\Ncalls him that! This isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.18,0:31:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's my fault that\Nl can't look after Sora well,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.06,0:31:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but l didn't want to kill her!\NI'm regretting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.36,0:31:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I understand. l did the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.44,0:31:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please, tell me what is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.80,0:32:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We don't know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.84,0:32:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}By the way, what is written on\Nthe piece of paper you drew?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.32,0:32:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.84,0:32:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l'll say this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.76,0:32:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.84,0:32:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}a bit taken aback.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.44,0:32:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Taken aback?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.27,0:32:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nothing is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.63,0:32:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes, the piece of paper is blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.79,0:32:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But I'm glad that it is blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.95,0:32:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Although l wasn't serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.55,0:32:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l still shouldn't have written\Nthe name of someone l want to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.07,0:33:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mrs lshizaki also said that\Nshe wrote her own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.99,0:33:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You wrote a name easily and\Nthere's something wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.43,0:33:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}It makes me think that\NI'm a horrible person,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.30,0:33:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx343\fscy397}and it makes me sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.76,0:33:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh? You are still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.48,0:33:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry, l applied for a day off\Nnext Thursday to go golfing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.12,0:33:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so l have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.04,0:33:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Go golfing on a weekday?\NWell-off, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.88,0:33:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm not well-off, that's why l go\Non a weekday, because it's cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.20,0:33:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.56,0:33:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Have a good evening.\N- Have a good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.60,0:33:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Darn...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.40,0:33:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l forgot them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.20,0:33:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.24,0:34:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Email from Toshiaki. No subject"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.60,0:34:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Will you send my golf clubs\Nto my office by post?"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.48,0:34:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- What is it?\N- Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.08,0:34:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l'm just wondering what you think\Nabout Airi and l getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.16,0:34:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm happy, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.04,0:34:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Besides the fact that\Nyou'll be her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.72,0:34:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.76,0:34:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, we aren't related by blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.88,0:34:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but l feel like I'm a dad\Nabout to marry off his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.32,0:35:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.00,0:35:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.12,0:35:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.44,0:35:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.80,0:35:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Why didn't you attend\Nthe residents' meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.24,0:35:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.28,0:35:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You asked us to\Nlook for the murderer ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.28,0:35:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.40,0:35:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm sorry. But l've already...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.20,0:35:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You told us the name you wrote\Nand the one on the piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.17,0:35:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Hey, you didn't tell them, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.01,0:35:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Hey, it isn't something\Nthat you can tell a random person!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.98,0:35:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.34,0:35:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'll tell you the name l wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.29,0:35:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It was Yoshihiko Hakamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.05,0:35:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What? So...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.97,0:35:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.73,0:35:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Gosh, what is going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I have joined them\Nto figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.76,0:36:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So we're doing that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.80,0:36:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.76,0:36:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We're looking for the person
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.72,0:36:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}who drew the paper\Nwith "Kayo Kojima" written.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.44,0:36:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Room 102's?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.78,0:36:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}And the person who has Room 104's\NMrs lshizaki's piece of paper too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.76,0:36:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.16,0:36:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If you want my help,\Nl can't do so now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.80,0:36:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The police suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.84,0:36:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Because l have no alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.88,0:36:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}on the night that\NMr and Mrs Akaike were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.16,0:36:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Of course l didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.68,0:36:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But there's a reason that\Nl can't tell them where l was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.40,0:36:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Let's start from the breakup scene\Nat the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.08,0:36:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But l haven't memorised\Nthe lines of that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.64,0:36:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Will someone remind her\Nif she's at a loss for words?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.20,0:37:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You want a prompter? l'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.68,0:37:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But you're new. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.36,0:37:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Let's begin and not waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.76,0:37:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Ready, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.24,0:37:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think neither of us is at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.88,0:37:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We each have our own view\Non what is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.52,0:37:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}they just aren't compatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.76,0:37:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If that's also what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.12,0:37:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l want to break up with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.40,0:37:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- No!\N- "No."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.04,0:37:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"l don't want to! lf we'll break up\Nwith a smile..."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.88,0:37:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Wait...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.44,0:37:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.00,0:37:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}She didn't say her line,\Nso l prompted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.12,0:37:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You just delayed a beat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.28,0:37:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes, l did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.48,0:37:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.12,0:37:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I didn't expect you\Nto delay a beat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.94,0:37:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If you don't mind, would you tell me\Nhow you plan to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.12,0:37:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He said he wanted to break up\Nand l was hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.42,0:38:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But looking at the development\Nof the whole story,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.25,0:38:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}the girl totally expected\Nwhat the guy would say
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.73,0:38:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}when she is here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.33,0:38:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}So instead of being hurt\Nby what he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.89,0:38:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}she would prevent him from saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.49,0:38:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Please say the line.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.21,0:38:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The last line.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.62,0:38:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.54,0:38:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Start here.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.34,0:38:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}If that's also what you think,\Nl want to--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.29,0:38:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I think you should say it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.33,0:38:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"I don't want to. lf we'll break up\Nwith a smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.64,0:38:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l would be a lot happier if we hate\Neach other to the core!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.50,0:38:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Then cue the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.06,0:38:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's a suggestion.\Nlt isn't absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.18,0:38:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}There's no correct answer in acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.06,0:38:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Let's do this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.58,0:38:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please let me learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.12,0:38:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.12,0:38:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh, I'm sorry. Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.26,0:38:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You're poking your nose\Ninto trouble like this, Ukita?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.94,0:39:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Please. This is for a girl\Nl love like my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.54,0:39:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I know where he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.02,0:39:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but won't you be in trouble\Nif the police sees you two meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.82,0:39:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It was years ago. l'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.92,0:39:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Tell absolutely no one\Nthat l told you where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.84,0:39:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.76,0:39:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Brothel Paradise"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.90,0:39:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Parking ticket"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.18,0:39:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.94,0:39:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I should've parked it\Nat the carpark.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.70,0:39:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"It is your turn to kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.74,0:39:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"lt is your turn to kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.36,0:40:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.84,0:40:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.64,0:40:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Excuse me.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.96,0:40:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Sorry about the other day.\N- Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.20,0:40:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I do want to help you,\Nbut l am extremely busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.80,0:40:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sure. l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.10,0:40:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.92,0:40:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.56,0:40:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I have information\Nthat will help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.12,0:40:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}that l refrained from telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.64,0:40:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.20,0:40:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's about Mr Kuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.60,0:40:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I had bumped into him once\Nat the lift...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.84,0:40:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l thought it was fishy,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.84,0:40:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so l checked afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.80,0:40:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It had been opened and closed\Nover and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.36,0:40:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mr Kuzumi probably did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.71,0:40:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You'd better not trust him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.08,0:41:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.80,0:41:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- It's okay.\N- lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.76,0:41:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I didn't expect...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.16,0:41:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}lt is messy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.20,0:41:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l've been busy going to school\Nand work.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.52,0:41:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But you have financial support,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.52,0:41:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Or you can't rent this flat\Non your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.80,0:41:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, my parents own this flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.52,0:41:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- You made me jealous!\N- You made me jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.84,0:41:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- We said it together.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.64,0:41:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Well, l've made a summary of\NNana's notes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.64,0:41:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.20,0:41:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}l do maths in university,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.56,0:41:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}sometimes l can't write\Nall the calculations in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.40,0:42:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.20,0:42:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Our main topic today...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.20,0:42:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.40,0:42:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Game participants,\Nname written, name drawn"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Murderer? Victims"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.63,0:42:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Residents not participating"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.79,0:42:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.95,0:42:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I somehow feel that some people\Ndon't like what we're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.79,0:42:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}so l think we'd better\Ntalk here from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.99,0:42:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.23,0:42:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Somehow, l feel that\Nwe can solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.80,0:42:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Game participants 101: Kuzumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Excuse me, Mr Kojima.\N- What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.48,0:42:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I forgot to tell you\Nthat you have a parcel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.04,0:42:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.08,0:42:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's bulky and heavy,\Nso it's at the distribution centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.80,0:42:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}It's fine. That's just my golf bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.56,0:42:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"But your wife sent it here."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.24,0:43:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Idiot, l don't want to see her,\Nthat's why l made her send it here."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.91,0:43:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}When l look at this,\Neveryone seems suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.59,0:43:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Even people who didn't participate\Nin the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.11,0:43:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Indeed. Like Room 501's Mr Sano.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.28,0:43:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He lives right next to Mrs Akaike.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.16,0:43:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But he's been the same as always,\Neven after the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.76,0:43:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}He always goes up the stairs\Nto the fifth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.36,0:43:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yes. lsn't he scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.12,0:43:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Is Mrs Kojima all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.48,0:43:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}I'm starting to get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.20,0:43:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Staff entrance"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.52,0:43:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Sender: Kayo Kojima"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.88,0:43:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mr Kojima, you must be using\Nsome fine quality clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.72,0:44:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}- Yeah. You want to see?\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.12,0:44:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mrs lshizaki too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.68,0:44:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Mrs lshizaki isn't on her own,\Nso I'm not worried yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.35,0:44:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Yeah... Mrs Kojima's husband\Nhasn't been going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.59,0:44:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}This will surprise\Na knowledgeable golf fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.32,0:44:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}But that happened to Mrs Akaike when\Nall three of them were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.21,0:44:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Somehow I'm getting worried now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.33,0:44:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Should we go see Mrs Kojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.26,0:44:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.98,0:44:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Do you know how awesome they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.21,0:45:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Your Turn to Kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.63,0:45:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Who drew my piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.47,0:45:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}We should tell the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.99,0:45:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}The people who threaten us\Nshould be different,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.41,0:45:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}but the handwriting is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.57,0:45:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}"Getting close to the truth"\Nl think someone is lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.69,0:46:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}She was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.61,0:46:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}You need a motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.69,0:46:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx343\fscy397}Nana... l hit the bull's eye!
